8. e-Rupee (CBDC)
•	Digital currency of India
•	Launched in December 2022
•	Uses smart contracts
•	Operates on a public blockchain
•	Developed using Distributed Ledger Technology (DLT)
•	Issued under CBDC by the Government of India
