17. Cryptocurrency
Cryptocurrency is a digital currency verified and maintained by a decentralized system.
•	World’s First Cryptocurrency: Bitcoin
•	Launched: 2008
________________________________________
18. Transaction Time
•	Bitcoin: ~10 minutes
•	Ethereum: ~2–3 minutes
________________________________________
19. Advantages of Cryptocurrency
•	No fraud
•	No identity theft
•	Immediate settlement
•	Global accessibility
•	Low transaction fees
