20. Bitcoin
•	Total Supply: 21,000,000 BTC
•	Current Supply: 19,590,512 BTC
Price History:
•	Highest Price: 10,263,984 (2025)
•	Lowest Price: 0.2 (2013)
Bitcoin is called the Mother Coin.
Other cryptocurrencies are called Altcoins.
________________________________________




21. Coin vs Token
Coin	Token
Has its own blockchain	Depends on another blockchain
Example: Bitcoin, Ethereum	Built on existing blockchains
Used mainly as digital currency	Used for utility purposes
Long-lasting	Short-term
Independent	Dependent
