KEY TAKEAWAYS
•	Blockchain is a secure, transparent, and decentralized ledger system
•	The blockchain market shows rapid global growth
•	Stable coins aim to become future digital currencies
•	Governments are increasing crypto regulation and awareness
•	Money has evolved toward decentralized digital finance
•	Blockchain powers the Fourth Industrial Revolution
•	Web 3.0 enables trust-based digital interaction
•	Smart contracts automate secure transactions
•	Cryptocurrencies enable fast, low-cost global payments
•	Bitcoin is the foundation of all cryptocurrencies
•	Coins and tokens serve different roles in blockchain ecosystems
